TopicTitle: To which bodies have you managed to send manned mission and return successfully?

Articles.Content:
I have seen thread about reaching some bodies. But how about manned missions?

I managed to perform such missions everywhere but Eve.

PS I would love to add more options, but polls are limited. Sorry.

E: Landing is required. Jool is on the list because of my stupidity.

Edited October 22, 2013 by El wonso
I've been on Mun, Minimus, Duna, Eve, Eeloo, Moho with Kerbin return. Have design for Tylo and Leithe landers, but have not yet tried it.
How do you do a manned mission to Jool, you can't land there? Or do you mean a manned mission that didn't have to land?
Yeah, does it include landing? Pretty important distinction in Eve's case.

Everything but Tylo and Jool, just because after I did Eve (which was back before we had lawn chairs and the mini lander can) I was kind of burned out building clever asparagus rockets. I haven't been to Laythe in a long time. I think the last time I went there I was using a mod to dock and refuel. I think I'll launch Tylo and Laythe missions at the next transfer window to Jool.

I have no interest in building a stock vehicle that can "land" on Jool. None.

This version (0.22) or any version?

Any version.

How do you do a manned mission to Jool, you can't land there? Or do you mean a manned mission that didn't have to land?

Landing is required, looks like im retarded. Any mod here to delete "Jool" choice?
